{"tid":1504012,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［集思廣益系列］ 麻煩大家供出黑社會平時蛇王的地方！！！","createTime":"2019-08-25T07:13:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T16:30:35.000Z","uid":247494,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7bab7c318159547a8b970beae32ef94694c2d2f8","tid":1504012,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:13:59.000Z","msg":"有人話俾我知，平時軍裝黑社會行咇一定唔會行足9個鐘，多數大部份時間搵竇坐下先（好聽就係叫落下簿）。<br />\n<br />\n我地點可浪費晒納稅人的錢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地盡市民責任，提醒佢地起身去做野，點可以週圍R<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟朋友係尼度拋磚引玉先，九龍灣地區：<br />\n<br />\n1. 麗晶停車場，我唔確定某一層，知道係類似雜物房，對出有更亭<br />\n2. 啟晴德朗，有一個商場係有屋宇署的辦事處，佢地係平日5點後，以及六日假期入面休息<br />\n3. 牛頭角下邨，貴X樓的屋宇署辦事處，又係上述時間內，佢地去蛇王<br />\n4. 淘大商場平台，管理處人員locker room <br />\n5. 彩德商場保安人員或管理處的休息室或locker room<br />\n6. 盈富樓地下看更控制室<br />\n7. 得寶花園停車場，入面有個細房，環境頗污糟，可以望到出面馬路<br />\n8. 啟業邨酒樓，以前個間的經理打晒龍通，而家尼間唔知有冇<br />\n9. 工廠區開達大廈，入口左側有小門駁上一個房 （順帶一提，佢地經常係康居買宵夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n10. 德福大廈下面清潔工人房<br />\n<br />\n大家記得得閒望一望，睇下有冇人蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔單止正規狗去蛇，輔狗都有份，但係佢地日頭大都數係做政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a832c82ef952de3dec28535d3a6208fef13f9d","tid":1504012,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:17:34.000Z","msg":"最大共通點，就係全部看更同狗蛇鼠一窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5f9c3d7326c8b41905a193a08934ef27585f9f0","tid":1504012,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:17:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fcall-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1Dgg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=29b1bccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/call-official-recognition-chinese-communist-party-terrorist-organization</a>"},{"pid":"e3551195433af78d123b3c8199637822c494737b","tid":1504012,"uid":2656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"而家佢地直情唔行咇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f21bcf8a89027bc906dbd8d284a5836cd52fb5","tid":1504012,"uid":22822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:21:03.000Z","msg":"佢地會係狗屋入面訓<br />\n<br />\n申利：有狗仔fd同我講"},{"pid":"b745da7d3b3b975ce137846e1bf5156142cef4df","tid":1504012,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:21:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a22366324e3405e3f0442ad0203594744f84ea00","tid":1504012,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3551195433af78d123b3c8199637822c494737b","tid":1504012,"uid":2656,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:19:47.000Z","msg":"而家佢地直情唔行咇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"唔行咇好似違反警察通例<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm